name: Unidentified_traveling_explorer
content: At some point in history, an unidentified traveling explorer visited the skies of Endor, a forested moon of the Moddell sector, in a hot air balloon. He or she crashed on top of the Explorer's Crag, a steep peak located near Endor's Happy Grove. The was trapped atop the Crag, and he or she ended up dying in the balloon's gondola. The explorer's skeleton was rediscovered around 3.5 ABY, when the Ewok named Wicket W. Warrick flew over the Explorer's Crag with his skin glider.
